## 7. ヒーロー — CSS背景画像パターン

```tsx
<section
  className="relative w-full min-h-[500px] md:min-h-[700px] flex flex-col justify-center bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat"
  style={{ backgroundImage: "url('/img/photos/hero.jpg')" }}
  aria-label="ヒーロー"
>
  <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50" aria-hidden />
  <div className="container mx-auto px-5 md:px-10 py-12 md:py-24 relative z-10">
    <h1 className="text-white text-[32px] md:text-[40px] font-bold drop-shadow-[0_1px_2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">...</h1>
  </div>
</section>
```

